rComments: Really amazing prof, smart pretty, funny ! Keeps class very interactive, u wont fall asleep. But vauge on what she wants from you on the tests and essay.
Very helpful and enthusiastic. Knowledgeable and fair. Fun lectures!

Although ok at teaching the subject, her tests/essays are so vaguely defined that it's pretty much guess what the prof/TA is thinking in order to do well. Would be better if she actually explained what she wanted from you rather then have you do poorly on a 40% essay.
